{
  "text": "Refs. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] introduced and then studied Adinkras, diagrams that encode the transformation rules of the component fields under the action of the supersymmetry generators Q 1 , . . . , Q N .",
  "correct_citation": {
